Package: pdfkeywords
Title: Extract keywords from PDF documents
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Steven",
           family = "Kambouris",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stevekambouris@fastmail.com")
Description: Search for keywords within PDF documents and return
    all found instances by page. Optionally, keywords can be returned in
    context, extracting a specified number of words before and after the
    keyword.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    pdftools,
    stringr,
    purrr,
    reshape2
